George D. NOELING, Jr., Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 13650. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. Dec. 28, 1951. P. Donald DeHoif, Jacksonville, Fla., for appellant. Ernest L. Duhaime, Asst. U. S. Atty., Miami, Fla., Damon G. Yerkes, Asst. U. S. Atty., Jacksonville, Fla., for appellee.

Before HOLMES, BORAH, and STRUM, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment-appealed from is affirmed.
